name: Cube Race (Punkinator2)
description:
Be the first to manuver your cube to the finish through increasingly difficult levels!

Wall jump up tricky cliffs

Watch out for the yellow objects, and the endless void below!

Gray objects are unstable, dont fall off!

This game is my first time dipping my toes in to the realm of game development. It started off as a class project, and I decided to turn it into a personal one. As it stands now, there are only 5 fairly short levels, but im planning on having 15-30, maybe even more.
